{"data":{"info":{"name":"James Jarvis","title":"Software Engineer, Explorer","email":{"address":"hello@jamesjarvis.io","subject":"Just saw your site!","body":"Loved your website! Care to exchange information?","text":"Say hi!"},"socials":[{"icon":"linkedin-in","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrjamesjarvis/","text":"Connect with me!"},{"icon":"github","url":"https://github.com/jamesjarvis","text":"Critique my code!"},{"icon":"keybase","url":"https://keybase.io/jamesjarvis","text":"View my proofs!"},{"icon":"instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jamjarvis/","text":"Follow me!"},{"icon":"youtube","url":"https://www.youtube.com/c/JamesJarvis1998","text":"Watch my videos!"}]},"bio":{"html":"<p>Hi, I'm James.\nI'm passionate about learning, building 'cool' stuff and travelling.\nThis year, 2020, I will be completing my <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://www.kent.ac.uk\" title=\"degree\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">degree</a> and getting back to work, who knows where I will be in 10 years?\nAt the moment, I can generally be found in <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canterbury\" title=\"Canterbury, UK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Canterbury, UK</a>, or online by clicking on any of the links below.\nIn my spare time you'll probably find me hopping on a cheap plane somewhere, camera in my hand and in search for an adventure.\nFeel free to reach out to me below regarding professional work, or just for a chat!\nMy (probably slightly out of date) <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"cv/resume.pdf\" title=\"CV is here\">CV is here</a>.\nAlso, if you're into that sort of stuff, you can find my public keys <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://keybase.pub/jamesjarvis/keys/\" title=\"here\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>"},"avatarImg":{"childImageSharp":{"avatar":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='4